        <div class="cyber-window-content">
            <div class="faq-header">
                <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
                <p>Find answers to common questions about Wirebase</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-content">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>What is Wirebase?</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Wirebase is a unique social platform that combines medieval dungeon fantasy aesthetics with cyberpunk digital interfaces. It's a place where users can connect, share content, and explore a digital realm inspired by both ancient and futuristic themes.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>How do I create an account?</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Click on "Plug into the Network" in the navigation menu to register. You'll need to provide a username, email address, and password. After registration, you can customize your profile with a display name, avatar, and custom glyph.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>What are bandwidth credits?</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Bandwidth credits are Wirebase's virtual currency. You earn them by participating in the community, creating content, and interacting with other users. They can be used to unlock special features, customize your profile, and boost your content visibility.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>What is the Scrapyard?</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>The Scrapyard (Nullspace) is where users can share digital artifacts, creations, code snippets, images, and other content. Think of it as a digital bazaar where users exchange ideas and creations.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>How do I customize my profile?</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Navigate to your profile page by clicking "Shell" in the navigation menu. From there, you can edit your profile information, upload an avatar, choose a custom glyph, and even customize your profile's HTML/CSS using the terminal interface.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>What are the different themes?</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Wirebase offers various visual themes that change the appearance of the site. These include dark-dungeon, retro-windows, broken-window, and more. You can change your theme in your profile settings.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>Is my data secure?</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>We take security seriously. Passwords are encrypted, and we implement various security measures to protect your data. For more information, please review our Privacy Policy.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>How can I report inappropriate content?</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Each post has a "Report" option that you can use to flag inappropriate content. Our moderation team reviews all reports and takes appropriate action according to our community guidelines.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <h3>How can I contact support?</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>For support inquiries, please email support@wirebase.city or use the contact form in your profile settings.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
